    "about": {
        "title": "About Us",
        "greeting": "Hello, I'm Rofaida Ayoub Damouni",
        "paragraph1": "I believe that every child has unique abilities and potential that deserve to be discovered and nurtured in the right way. Through my experience in occupational therapy, I strive to support children in developing their motor, sensory, cognitive, and social skills through enjoyable approaches based on play, exploration, and interaction.",
        "paragraph2": "Because play is a child's world and first language, I carefully select purposeful toys and educational resources that help children learn, explore, and build self-confidence. I also offer parents guidance and support so they can be active partners in their children's development.",
        "paragraph3": "That is why we provide carefully selected educational and developmental toys that combine enjoyment with meaningful benefits and help children acquire the skills they need at every stage of growth.",
        "paragraph4": "My mission is to help build a confident and independent generation capable of reaching its full potential, and to turn every moment of play into an opportunity for learning and growth.",
